631
00:44:29.003 --> 00:44:30.037
Okay.

632
00:44:30.070 --> 00:44:31.071
Uh...

633
00:44:31.872 --> 00:44:33.874
Okay. Right there.

634
00:44:35.242 --> 00:44:36.310
