648
00:46:11.872 --> 00:46:13.941
-You are the problem.
-You wanna get in my face?

649
00:46:13.974 --> 00:46:15.242
-You wanna threaten me?
-I'm not...

650
00:46:15.276 --> 00:46:16.844
