651
00:46:16.877 --> 00:46:18.312
You're barking up
the wrong tree. Okay?

652
00:46:18.345 --> 00:46:20.814
This whole victim persona
that you're taking on.

653
00:46:20.848 --> 00:46:22.383
it might have
the police fooled.

654
00:46:22.416 --> 00:46:23.951
it might have
the school fooled...

655
00:46:23.984 --> 00:46:25.319
