656
00:46:27.622 --> 00:46:29.557
-Stop thinking of yourself!
-Marcus?

657
00:46:29.591 --> 00:46:31.992
You and I are gonna
have a conversation right...

658
00:46:32.026 --> 00:46:33.528
-[Marcus grunting]
-[Justine straining]

659
00:46:35.563 --> 00:46:37.164
