664
00:46:57.251 --> 00:46:59.219
[panting. growling]

665
00:47:00.287 --> 00:47:01.322
Hey!

666
00:47:04.124 --> 00:47:05.560
[growling]

667
00:47:08.929 --> 00:47:10.831
[snarling]

668
00:47:11.198 --> 00:47:12.232
[shouts. growls]

669
00:47:18.506 --> 00:47:19.873
[shrieking]

670
00:47:25.680 --> 00:47:26.947
