715
00:49:03.010 --> 00:49:05.279
Anniversary lunch?

716
00:49:06.614 --> 00:49:08.182
Yep.

717
00:49:08.215 --> 00:49:10.083
That's nice.
Well. congratulations and...

718
00:49:10.117 --> 00:49:12.286
