724
00:49:21.596 --> 00:49:23.430
Well. just starting
my shift here.

725
00:49:23.464 --> 00:49:24.498
Roger that.

726
00:49:27.301 --> 00:49:28.502
[man talking nearby]

727
00:49:43.585 --> 00:49:45.720
["Don't Be Scared"
